{"tid":1642286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（回帶）香港仔警署槍擊事件","createTime":"2019-10-09T16:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:03:04.000Z","uid":242029,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b83002f645733949aca8eeeb40d20f476bb13b48","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"1997年11月初，一名警察在香港仔警署開槍擊斃一名接受調查的市民，重溫當年的報道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">槍擊事件於前晚九時許發生，一隊港島衝鋒隊警員於石排灣邨搜查死者陳國強，發現他沒有帶身份證，於是將他帶往香港仔警署盤問，不久死者在接見室內身中三槍死亡。而涉嫌開槍的警員，目前送往青山醫院檢驗。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港島總區指揮官梁豐順說：「這名警員在1994年已經開始接受警隊的心理專家治療。1996年初，心理專家證實他是完全康復。」<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，涉嫌開槍警員27歲。一隊港島衝鋒隊警員，昨晚於石排灣村搜查這名24歲姓陳男子。由於男子沒帶身份證，警員於是將他帶去香港仔警署，涉嫌開槍的警員將男子帶到接見室盤問，不久就傳出槍聲。<br />\n<br />\n總共開了六槍，有四槍在接見室內開，其中兩槍打中男子頸部、一槍打中右肩，該男子由於失血過多致死。涉嫌警員後來向接見室外面再開多兩槍，但沒有打中人。他後來被其他警員制服。<br />\n<br />\n警方派代表見完死者陳國強的家人後說，和對方談過賠償等問題。<br />\n<br />\n警民關係主任梁琼燕表示︰「他要求就希望我們警方檢討一下，會否有重複的事件發生。他不希望將來有重複的事件發生。」<br />\n<br />\n被問及有否要求其他、譬如賠償或責任追究時，梁琼燕答︰「賠償有，有暴力傷亡賠償，我們會替他安排申請。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一直都係軍政府 dklm</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 唔見人 831 打死人 101 槍殺人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/newsfile/5d9be321e603835a301c86ce/香港仔警署槍擊事件1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fnewsfile%2F5d9be321e603835a301c86ce%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B61&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5x4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=b60fca0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/newsfile/5d9be321e603835a301c86ce/香港仔警署槍擊事件1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/newsfile/5d9d50c1e603831405913f8b/香港仔警署槍擊事件2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fnewsfile%2F5d9d50c1e603831405913f8b%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B62&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5x4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=018ec217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/newsfile/5d9d50c1e603831405913f8b/香港仔警署槍擊事件2</a>"},{"pid":"5dc80e9ba573e829d27d6e972cc0a0425b936690","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83002f645733949aca8eeeb40d20f476bb13b48","tid