ets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7eba024f07ded2655e0aa046664ddeda2b8544a","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊  2/10</span>"},{"pid":"4219c66adc6aa680d4ede153e67ec30a82ec0214","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊 3/10</span>"},{"pid":"6548edced5b14d813a5a66a44f7cb30761ed1afb","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊  4/10</span>"},{"pid":"3bda4617ca4a4ef94af310b78fe83a528e6ca7e1","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊  5/10</span>"},{"pid":"a91021cded1313adf8382752de8b22a8810d5cee","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊  6/10</span>"},{"pid":"37fcc2eab1c47bc20a09daf1272dd97cf51048ec","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊  7/10</span>"},{"pid":"d56e67702481bc29316a97213502f10db2675c12","tid":1642286,"uid":123205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3YfQTqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3YfQTqQ.jpg&h=bce221de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd62309fdc55667a9cc304e8c14eb92de8c293b2","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊  8/10</span>"},{"pid":"b8195c02bbdcd7b49e64557f827ab081dbb00992","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊  9/10</span>"},{"pid":"dc57117ed7681d8fc41802275ecab1d9c18db07b","tid":1642286,"uid":39277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"件事發生係97年7月之後"},{"pid":"a06e9c2a1b25713a2f618725e3cfe2818f8509d1","tid":1642286,"uid":242029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊  10/10</span>"},{"pid":"e74ce73d23ea32caa37cc968cdfe711095e803b4","tid":1642286,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"Another case. CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200609/06/P200609060284.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200609%2F06%2FP200609060284.htm&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5x4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=0351b84e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200609/06/P200609060284.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方調查香港仔開槍案件<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n警方現正調查今日（九月六日）晚上在香港仔發生的開槍案件。案中一名四十四歲警署警長在香港仔海傍道附近一條行人隧道內被一名休班警員槍傷。<br />\n<br />\n晚上約六時三十分，警方接報指一名警署警長在香港仔海傍道附近一條行人隧道內被一名三十九歲休班警員槍傷。該名休班警員於今日下午被其家人報失。<br />\n<br />\n初步調查顯示，該名休班警員於今日中午在家人陪同下乘的士離開瑪麗醫院，當的士到達田灣嘉禾街時逃離的士，留下家人在的士內。<br />\n<br />\n他的家人於下午約二時十五分向警方報案指他失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上約六時三十分，一名警署警長與另一名警員在祟文街巡邏時，與該名休班警員相遇，但該休班警員立刻逃走。<br />\n<br />\n  警署警長與巡邏警員最後在香港仔海傍道附近一行人隧道內截停該名休班警員，並發生糾纏，混亂中該休班警員搶去另一名警員的配槍並向警署警長開了一槍。<br />\n<br />\n  警署警長右大腿中槍被送瑪麗醫院救治。<br />\n<br />\n  該名休班警員即場被捕，其後被帶往香港仔警署作一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n  警方西區警區重案組現正調查此宗案件。<br />\n<br />\n續警察公共關係科續新聞公布六號<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n２００６年９月６日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間２２時２６分"},{"pid":"dcf2a26636b1c8c9d0567538fa8e629583105316","tid":1642286,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"痴線警"}]}